@DATABASE "Underwurlde"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - U - Underwurlde"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - U
                   ====================================

                                Underwurlde
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(59375,0)"}          59375,0
@{"Infinite Gems " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38042,33)"}          38042,33
@{"No Enemies    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(45018,201)"}          45018,201
@{"??????????????" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(59591,0)"}          59591,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(36980,255)"}          36980,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I never was much good at this game, so I can't
                         see if the "Mystery" POKE has any effect at
                         all, but I've left it here, so try it and see!


                         The "Lives = x" and "Infinite Lives" were by
                         me. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
